reviewText: Cute musical about young innocent love.  Group of teenagers, each with their own scars, find warmth and love through support of each other.  It is through music they achieve their dreams.
Would have given it 5 stars but the ending was a bit weak for my taste.  Loved the cast - music was a lot of fun!

I watched this on DramaFever, and fell in love with the story! The basis of story line is about these group of students are psychologically injured, and heal through the music, but with a splash of romance thrown in! XD
